1
00:01:43,065 --> 00:01:45,105
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

2
00:01:50,185 --> 00:01:53,625
Jiaxu, what will you be doing

3
00:01:54,105 --> 00:01:55,185
while I study?

4
00:01:56,585 --> 00:01:57,585
I will

5
00:01:57,665 --> 00:01:58,865
just be sitting here.

6
00:02:00,985 --> 00:02:02,185
You'll just be sitting here?

7
00:02:02,825 --> 00:02:05,265
I want to look at you more.

8
00:02:36,305 --> 00:02:37,465
Is that enough for you?

9
00:02:38,305 --> 00:02:40,425
If you don't leave,
I won't be able to focus.

10
00:02:55,305 --> 00:02:56,745
Can't I stay here

11
00:02:59,345 --> 00:03:01,305
without saying a word?

12
00:03:02,865 --> 00:03:04,825
You said you won't

13
00:03:04,905 --> 00:03:06,345
get in the way of my studies.

14
00:03:17,705 --> 00:03:18,745
All right then.

15
00:03:21,425 --> 00:03:23,145
You're such a cruel girlfriend.

16
00:03:26,025 --> 00:03:27,505
Go ahead and study.

17
00:03:34,145 --> 00:03:35,225
What do you want to eat?

18
00:03:35,305 --> 00:03:36,505
I'll make you something tasty.

19
00:03:37,385 --> 00:03:39,225
Zhizhi has been studying hard.

20
00:03:44,025 --> 00:03:45,625
I'm fine with anything

21
00:03:45,705 --> 00:03:47,505
as long as you make it.

22
00:03:49,985 --> 00:03:51,025
Okay.

23
00:03:51,105 --> 00:03:53,345
Then let me know if you need anything.

24
00:03:55,345 --> 00:03:56,505
Jiaxu.

25
00:03:56,585 --> 00:03:58,985
Why does it feel like
you're taking care of a kid?

26
00:03:59,785 --> 00:04:00,665
That's what I'm doing.

27
00:04:01,625 --> 00:04:02,825
I'm afraid

28
00:04:02,905 --> 00:04:04,745
someone might steal my kiddo.

29
00:04:23,185 --> 00:04:25,185
CHAPTER 18, CAPTIVATED

30
00:04:25,265 --> 00:04:26,825
THE TASTE OF FIRST LOVE

31
00:04:44,465 --> 00:04:45,545
Jiaxu.

32
00:04:46,185 --> 00:04:48,185
I think your cooking is really delicious.

33
00:04:49,585 --> 00:04:50,585
Do you like it?

34
00:04:51,625 --> 00:04:53,185
Not just anyone gets to taste it.

35
00:04:53,705 --> 00:04:54,905
You're the first one.

36
00:05:07,705 --> 00:05:09,305
-Are you full?
-I'm full.

37
00:05:12,185 --> 00:05:13,545
Are you full?

38
00:05:14,225 --> 00:05:15,545
Are you full too?

39
00:05:16,265 --> 00:05:17,905
Give it to me. I'll do the dishes.

40
00:05:18,985 --> 00:05:20,665
Get some rest. I can do the dishes.

41
00:05:20,745 --> 00:05:22,065
Let me help you with something.

42
00:05:22,145 --> 00:05:23,425
You already cooked.

43
00:05:23,505 --> 00:05:24,825
So I'll do the dishes.

44
00:05:25,385 --> 00:05:26,665
You can rest.

45
00:05:29,425 --> 00:05:30,545
Okay.

46
00:05:30,625 --> 00:05:32,385
-I'll bring you the dishes.
-Okay.

47
00:05:36,785 --> 00:05:38,105
Just leave them here.

48
00:05:48,305 --> 00:05:49,465
Here.

49
00:06:10,945 --> 00:06:12,545
Don't you know how to do housework?

50
00:06:12,625 --> 00:06:14,025
Why don't I take over?

51
00:06:14,665 --> 00:06:16,465
I'll learn after doing it a few times.

52
00:06:17,225 --> 00:06:18,585
Why do you need to learn?

53
00:06:18,665 --> 00:06:20,985
I never said you have to learn.

54
00:06:21,705 --> 00:06:23,545
I can't let you do everything yourself

55
00:06:23,625 --> 00:06:24,505
in the future.

56
00:06:28,545 --> 00:06:30,185
I am thinking

57
00:06:31,105 --> 00:06:32,385
too far ahead.

58
00:06:32,945 --> 00:06:33,865
I know.

59
00:06:35,865 --> 00:06:36,825
So after this,

60
00:06:37,545 --> 00:06:39,225
do you want to chat with me

61
00:06:39,305 --> 00:06:40,545
or rest for a while?

62
00:06:43,385 --> 00:06:45,185
I haven't finished studying.

63
00:06:45,745 --> 00:06:46,785
You'll study?

64
00:06:47,305 --> 00:06:48,905
Aren't you sleepy? Take a nap.

65
00:06:48,985 --> 00:06:50,105
I'm not sleepy.

66
00:06:52,345 --> 00:06:54,425
You sure are serious about your studies.

67
00:06:57,185 --> 00:06:58,705
I'm aiming for a scholarship.

68
00:07:00,305 --> 00:07:01,465
Okay.

69
00:07:01,545 --> 00:07:03,225
Zhizhi is the most ambitious.

70
00:07:04,225 --> 00:07:05,665
I'll help you with the dishes.

71
00:08:31,345 --> 00:08:32,705
I'm sleepy.

72
00:08:35,105 --> 00:08:36,985
Why am I so sleepy?

73
00:09:08,505 --> 00:09:09,465
Hello.

74
00:09:10,425 --> 00:09:11,745
It has been a long time.

75
00:09:25,345 --> 00:09:26,705
I'll nap for five minutes.

76
00:09:26,785 --> 00:09:28,225
I should take a five-minute nap.

77
00:09:28,785 --> 00:09:30,105
Five minutes will do.

78
00:09:41,905 --> 00:09:43,145
Do you want water, Zhizhi?

79
00:09:43,825 --> 00:09:44,825
I'm coming in.

80
00:10:01,145 --> 00:10:02,105
Where is she?

81
00:10:02,745 --> 00:10:03,625
Where did she go?

82
00:10:13,705 --> 00:10:14,825
What are you doing?

83
00:10:18,785 --> 00:10:19,625
I am

84
00:10:20,265 --> 00:10:21,145
memorizing vocabulary.

85
00:10:21,705 --> 00:10:23,465
Why are you doing it on the floor?

86
00:10:24,025 --> 00:10:26,185
This is more exciting,
so I won't feel sleepy.

87
00:10:27,145 --> 00:10:28,105
Exciting?

88
00:10:48,425 --> 00:10:49,665
Do you like excitement?

89
00:10:53,785 --> 00:10:55,625
Then let's make it exciting.

90
00:11:07,305 --> 00:11:09,625
Duan Jiaxu, why are you being naughty?

91
00:11:13,025 --> 00:11:14,425
We're already together.

92
00:11:15,025 --> 00:11:16,665
How can it be called naughty?

93
00:11:31,585 --> 00:11:32,865
Tell me.

94
00:11:33,505 --> 00:11:35,345
How did you end up on the floor?

95
00:11:38,145 --> 00:11:39,785
I was studying.

96
00:11:40,745 --> 00:11:43,105
Then I got sleepy and wanted to nap.

97
00:11:44,265 --> 00:11:47,345
But I was adamant earlier about studying.

98
00:11:47,425 --> 00:11:48,265
I…

99
00:11:48,905 --> 00:11:51,185
If you saw me sleeping,

100
00:11:51,265 --> 00:11:54,105
I was afraid you would think
I was ignoring you, so…

101
00:11:55,585 --> 00:11:57,025
I'm not that petty.

102
00:11:57,985 --> 00:11:58,945
Take a nap.

103
00:11:59,025 --> 00:12:00,065
I'll wake you up later.

104
00:12:06,145 --> 00:12:07,145
Lie down.

105
00:12:12,185 --> 00:12:14,825
Well, won't you feel bored?

106
00:12:16,705 --> 00:12:17,865
A little bit.

107
00:12:20,905 --> 00:12:21,865
But

108
00:12:23,305 --> 00:12:25,545
I'm already happy
that you came here to study.

109
00:12:29,905 --> 00:12:31,105
Take your nap now.

110
00:12:42,505 --> 00:12:43,545
What's the matter?

111
00:12:45,745 --> 00:12:46,945
Jiaxu.

112
00:12:48,905 --> 00:12:49,945
It's not

113
00:12:50,785 --> 00:12:52,465
that I don't like you

114
00:12:52,545 --> 00:12:53,905
being like this.

115
00:12:54,505 --> 00:12:56,385
It's because I get nervous

116
00:12:56,465 --> 00:12:57,545
when you get close to me.

117
00:12:57,625 --> 00:12:59,105
I don't know why either.

118
00:12:59,785 --> 00:13:00,625
So…

119
00:13:02,425 --> 00:13:04,105
I just want to tell you

120
00:13:04,185 --> 00:13:05,985
that it's not that I don't like you.

121
00:13:14,625 --> 00:13:16,065
That means you like me.

122
00:13:23,545 --> 00:13:24,625
Well…

123
00:13:25,785 --> 00:13:27,865
I just don't like being too…

124
00:13:32,105 --> 00:13:32,985
I get it.

125
00:13:33,985 --> 00:13:35,065
If so,

126
00:13:36,305 --> 00:13:37,625
we'll see how it goes.

127
00:13:41,145 --> 00:13:42,385
Take your nap.

128
00:13:55,745 --> 00:13:57,105
Call me if you need anything.

129
00:14:33,945 --> 00:14:35,065
You eat it.

130
00:14:41,305 --> 00:14:43,065
Maybe I should have one.

131
00:14:45,505 --> 00:14:47,065
What flavor do you want?

132
00:14:47,145 --> 00:14:48,385
Any flavor will do.

133
00:14:49,625 --> 00:14:50,465
This one then.

134
00:15:02,425 --> 00:15:04,625
Giving candy or holding hands?

135
00:15:17,145 --> 00:15:19,025
Holding hands or holding hands?

136
00:15:27,465 --> 00:15:28,825
Well, holding hands it is.

137
00:15:34,745 --> 00:15:36,945
Why are you asking this so seriously?

138
00:15:39,905 --> 00:15:41,625
Can I hold your hand?

139
00:16:31,825 --> 00:16:32,905
Have you been

140
00:16:33,785 --> 00:16:35,105
applying for internships?

141
00:16:38,705 --> 00:16:40,945
I've sent my resume to several companies,

142
00:16:41,025 --> 00:16:42,745
but I haven't received any replies.

143
00:16:43,345 --> 00:16:45,305
Why do you suddenly want an internship?

144
00:16:50,225 --> 00:16:51,225
Well…

145
00:16:53,345 --> 00:16:54,545
I want to give it a try.

146
00:17:02,545 --> 00:17:03,625
Thank you.

147
00:17:13,265 --> 00:17:14,105
Jiaxu.

148
00:17:16,704 --> 00:17:18,305
When people hold hands,

149
00:17:19,224 --> 00:17:21,545
they either do it when crossing the street

150
00:17:21,625 --> 00:17:23,385
or by accident.

151
00:17:23,944 --> 00:17:25,265
No one would do what you did

152
00:17:25,865 --> 00:17:27,145
and ask to hold hands.

153
00:17:27,985 --> 00:17:29,625
That was so strange.

154
00:17:33,345 --> 00:17:34,545
I chose to do that

155
00:17:34,625 --> 00:17:35,945
because I made you upset

156
00:17:36,025 --> 00:17:37,705
when I kissed you

157
00:17:37,785 --> 00:17:38,865
without asking.

158
00:17:38,945 --> 00:17:40,345
I wasn't upset.

159
00:17:43,305 --> 00:17:44,265
I was

160
00:17:46,185 --> 00:17:47,105
nervous.

161
00:17:50,985 --> 00:17:51,945
I know.

162
00:17:52,945 --> 00:17:53,905
Now,

163
00:17:54,745 --> 00:17:56,385
you suddenly became my girlfriend.

164
00:17:57,185 --> 00:17:58,745
Do you find it hard to get used to?

165
00:17:59,545 --> 00:18:00,545
Not at all.

166
00:18:00,625 --> 00:18:02,105
Don't imagine things.

167
00:18:15,225 --> 00:18:17,185
Have I not told you this?

168
00:18:22,345 --> 00:18:23,745
I really like you.

169
00:18:32,065 --> 00:18:33,305
I do like you a lot.

170
00:19:04,545 --> 00:19:05,385
Me too.

171
00:19:07,265 --> 00:19:08,305
I like you a lot.

172
00:19:43,745 --> 00:19:44,745
DUAN JIAXU

173
00:19:44,825 --> 00:19:46,185
You have to wake up early tomorrow,

174
00:19:46,265 --> 00:19:47,345
so go to bed early.

175
00:19:47,945 --> 00:19:48,825
Good night.

176
00:20:11,545 --> 00:20:12,385
Hello?

177
00:20:12,465 --> 00:20:13,505
Hey, Duan Jiaxu.

178
00:20:14,265 --> 00:20:16,265
I'm going to Yihe
for work again next week.

179
00:20:16,345 --> 00:20:18,065
Treat me to something delicious this time.

180
00:20:18,145 --> 00:20:19,945
Don't give me fried chicken and milk tea.

181
00:20:20,505 --> 00:20:21,825
Okay, no problem.

182
00:20:21,905 --> 00:20:23,665
I'll give you a seafood feast this time.

183
00:20:23,745 --> 00:20:24,825
How about that?

184
00:20:25,385 --> 00:20:26,825
Why are you suddenly so generous?

185
00:20:27,625 --> 00:20:29,945
There must be a reason
for this abnormal behavior.

186
00:20:30,025 --> 00:20:32,705
Buddy, could it be

187
00:20:33,985 --> 00:20:35,065
that you've gotten the girl?

188
00:20:37,865 --> 00:20:38,705
Yes.

189
00:20:38,785 --> 00:20:40,545
Way to go!

190
00:20:41,465 --> 00:20:43,105
You have to thank me for this.

191
00:20:43,185 --> 00:20:44,945
You couldn't have done it without me.

192
00:20:45,025 --> 00:20:46,785
Yes, so you can

193
00:20:46,865 --> 00:20:49,225
order anything you want to eat, okay?

194
00:20:52,185 --> 00:20:53,025
How nice.

195
00:20:53,105 --> 00:20:56,065
That means you might get married
earlier than Sang Yan.

196
00:20:56,145 --> 00:20:57,465
We should rile him up a bit.

197
00:20:57,545 --> 00:20:58,825
I can't stand him anymore.

198
00:20:59,745 --> 00:21:01,185
No, I'm going to do it now.

199
00:21:02,905 --> 00:21:04,505
Hey, what are you doing?

200
00:21:04,585 --> 00:21:05,425
QIAN FEI

201
00:21:05,505 --> 00:21:06,945
Jiaxu has a girlfriend now!

202
00:21:07,025 --> 00:21:07,945
And I made it happen!

203
00:21:08,025 --> 00:21:10,265
I require worshiping applause
and admiration now!

204
00:21:10,345 --> 00:21:11,305
To Sang Yan.

205
00:21:19,025 --> 00:21:20,385
Buddy,

206
00:21:20,465 --> 00:21:22,385
I have to admit something to you.

207
00:21:22,465 --> 00:21:24,185
I haven't been completely honest with you.

208
00:21:24,745 --> 00:21:25,945
What is it?

209
00:21:27,185 --> 00:21:28,865
You know this girl too.

210
00:21:30,705 --> 00:21:31,705
I know her?

211
00:21:32,745 --> 00:21:34,225
You're in Yihe and I'm in Nanwu.

212
00:21:34,305 --> 00:21:35,265
How do I know her?

213
00:21:36,465 --> 00:21:38,425
You didn't meet her in Yihe.

214
00:21:38,505 --> 00:21:39,825
Not in Yihe?

215
00:21:40,905 --> 00:21:43,425
Do we have any juniors who work in Yihe?

216
00:21:43,505 --> 00:21:44,985
I don't recall any.

217
00:21:45,065 --> 00:21:47,105
She's studying at a university in Yihe.

218
00:21:52,425 --> 00:21:53,505
Studying?

219
00:21:54,625 --> 00:21:56,105
Don't tell me

220
00:21:56,825 --> 00:21:57,985
it's Sang Zhi.

221
00:22:01,865 --> 00:22:03,225
Okay, that's all. Bye.

222
00:22:03,305 --> 00:22:04,145
What?

223
00:22:06,785 --> 00:22:07,785
Seriously, man.

224
00:22:07,865 --> 00:22:09,825
I really have to thank you for this.

225
00:22:09,905 --> 00:22:11,145
Why are you thanking me?

226
00:22:11,665 --> 00:22:12,825
Did I help you with anything?

227
00:22:12,905 --> 00:22:14,185
When you first met Sang Zhi,

228
00:22:14,265 --> 00:22:15,985
she was a short 14-year-old kid.

229
00:22:16,065 --> 00:22:17,065
How could you…

230
00:22:19,905 --> 00:22:20,785
Tell me.

231
00:22:21,425 --> 00:22:22,785
Have you told Sang Yan about this?

232
00:22:24,505 --> 00:22:25,705
I haven't told him yet.

233
00:22:26,865 --> 00:22:28,465
When are you planning to tell him?

234
00:22:28,545 --> 00:22:30,905
I plan to go to Nanwu
and tell him in person.

235
00:22:32,505 --> 00:22:33,865
I think it's better

236
00:22:34,665 --> 00:22:36,905
to tell him in person about this.

237
00:22:36,985 --> 00:22:38,065
That's right.

238
00:22:38,145 --> 00:22:39,345
I have to recall that message.

239
00:22:39,425 --> 00:22:40,825
He'll keep asking me if he sees it.

240
00:22:41,865 --> 00:22:42,865
Hey.

241
00:22:43,905 --> 00:22:45,465
Sang Yan is calling me.

242
00:22:45,545 --> 00:22:46,865
Why did you even send that text?

243
00:22:47,785 --> 00:22:48,745
Answer it.

244
00:22:48,825 --> 00:22:51,225
If you don't,
there's no way to explain it.

245
00:22:51,305 --> 00:22:52,865
Listen, I have nothing to do with this.

246
00:22:52,945 --> 00:22:54,545
You need to be honest with him. Bye now.

247
00:22:54,625 --> 00:22:56,625
How about this? Do it with me.

248
00:22:56,705 --> 00:22:57,665
If you're not there,

249
00:22:57,745 --> 00:22:59,985
I really might say the wrong thing.

250
00:23:00,745 --> 00:23:02,905
SANG YAN INVITES YOU TO A GROUP CALL

251
00:23:02,985 --> 00:23:04,545
OTHERS JOINING THE CALL

252
00:23:04,625 --> 00:23:06,065
Hey, Duan Jiaxu.

253
00:23:06,145 --> 00:23:08,265
Did you lose your marbles somewhere

254
00:23:08,345 --> 00:23:10,265
for you to ask Qian Fei
to help you get a girl?

255
00:23:11,505 --> 00:23:12,665
What's wrong with asking me?

256
00:23:13,385 --> 00:23:15,545
No, you should ask me about these things.

257
00:23:15,625 --> 00:23:16,585
How could you go to him?

258
00:23:16,665 --> 00:23:18,305
But then again, I don't go after girls.

259
00:23:18,385 --> 00:23:20,465
Usually, the girls go wild for me.

260
00:23:20,545 --> 00:23:22,745
Qian Fei is an expert at pursuing girls.

261
00:23:22,825 --> 00:23:24,185
Get lost.

262
00:23:24,825 --> 00:23:25,785
Tell me

263
00:23:25,865 --> 00:23:28,025
who the unlucky girl is.

264
00:23:32,585 --> 00:23:33,785
She is indeed pretty unlucky.

265
00:23:34,385 --> 00:23:36,585
But I still need to thank Qian Fei

266
00:23:36,665 --> 00:23:37,665
for his help this time.

267
00:23:38,305 --> 00:23:39,545
What does it have to do with me?

268
00:23:39,625 --> 00:23:40,505
I…

269
00:23:40,585 --> 00:23:42,425
Duan Jiaxu, how could I have helped?

270
00:23:43,025 --> 00:23:44,785
Besides, I didn't pursue my wife.

271
00:23:44,865 --> 00:23:46,145
My wife pursued me.

272
00:23:47,105 --> 00:23:48,625
Did you really not help him with it?

273
00:23:49,545 --> 00:23:51,225
Qian Fei, why are you so worked up?

274
00:23:51,305 --> 00:23:52,985
Am I?

275
00:23:53,065 --> 00:23:54,985
Why would I be? I don't know anything.

276
00:23:56,105 --> 00:23:58,185
Qian Fei, you're acting a bit strange.

277
00:23:58,265 --> 00:24:00,145
You could brag about this for three years,

278
00:24:00,225 --> 00:24:01,745
but you're actually denying it.

279
00:24:02,545 --> 00:24:04,385
Maybe I've become mature tonight.

280
00:24:04,465 --> 00:24:05,505
I can't believe you two.

281
00:24:05,585 --> 00:24:07,265
Are you shutting me out? Fine.

282
00:24:07,345 --> 00:24:08,545
