00:39:21,025 --> 00:39:22,705
Forget it. I'll retake it next semester.

570
00:39:22,785 --> 00:39:25,105
But tonight, everyone must celebrate.

571
00:39:25,185 --> 00:39:26,505
Everyone must go. Do you hear me?

572
00:39:26,585 --> 00:39:28,145
