575
00:39:33,785 --> 00:39:34,945
No.

576
00:39:35,025 --> 00:39:36,225
Why not?

577
00:39:36,305 --> 00:39:37,585
Doing an internship is good.

578
00:39:37,665 --> 00:39:38,545
You can start working.

579
00:39:38,625 --> 00:39:40,545
-That's right.
-They do want me to intern.

580
00:39:40,625 --> 00:39:42,745
They just don't want me to do it in Yihe.

581
00:39:43,425 --> 00:39:45,305
They found an internship in Nanwu for me

582
00:39:45,385 --> 00:39:46,385
and want me to go back.

583
00:39:47,145 --> 00:39:48,985
Then go back to Nanwu.

584
00:39:51,905 --> 00:39:54,585
But I still feel that staying in Yihe

585
00:39:54,665 --> 00:39:57,545
may get me more opportunities.

586
00:39:57,625 --> 00:39:59,865
Do you think Yihe
has more job opportunities

587
00:39:59,945 --> 00:40:02,625
or do you just prefer your boyfriend
who is in Yihe?

588
00:40:02,705 --> 00:40:04,065
Stop teasing me.

589
00:40:05,705 --> 00:40:06,905
Hello?

590
00:40:12,985 --> 00:40:13,865
Yes, that's me.

591
00:40:16,025 --> 00:40:16,865
All right.

592
00:40:17,505 --> 00:40:19,105
Okay, I see.

593
00:40:21,745 --> 00:40:23,145
-What is it?
-What's up?

594
00:40:25,425 --> 00:40:26,785
I passed my interview.

595
00:40:44,425 --> 00:40:46,225
I've looked at the file you sent.

596
00:40:46,305 --> 00:40:48,905
I'll work on it some more tonight.

597
00:40:49,585 --> 00:40:50,585
Bye.

598
00:40:56,065 --> 00:40:57,385
Hi. Excuse me.

599
00:40:57,465 --> 00:40:59,425
Can you tell me where I can find a café?

600
00:41:00,465 --> 00:41:02,425
There's a nice café over there.

601
00:41:02,505 --> 00:41:03,745
Over there, right?

602
00:41:03,825 --> 00:41:04,865
Okay.

603
00:41:06,465 --> 00:41:08,225
Can I add you on WeChat?

604
00:41:16,305 --> 00:41:17,265
Sorry.

605
00:41:17,345 --> 00:41:20,465
If my girlfriend finds out,

606
00:41:21,025 --> 00:41:22,105
I'll be dead meat.

607
00:41:23,425 --> 00:41:24,585
Sorry for bothering you.

608
00:41:24,665 --> 00:41:25,505
No problem.

609
00:41:41,545 --> 00:41:42,785
Are you angry?

610
00:41:44,505 --> 00:41:45,385
No.

611
00:41:46,345 --> 00:41:47,185
Drink it.

612
00:41:50,545 --> 00:41:52,145
If not, why won't you look at me?

613
00:41:54,985 --> 00:41:56,305
And you're even pouting.

614
00:41:59,025 --> 00:42:01,025
It's just a WeChat request.
Why would I be angry?

615
00:42:02,385 --> 00:42:03,465
Are you really not angry?

616
00:42:05,985 --> 00:42:06,865
No.

617
00:42:06,945 --> 00:42:08,065
Are you jealous?

618
00:42:08,145 --> 00:42:09,385
No.

619
00:42:11,665 --> 00:42:12,545
Seeing you like this,

620
00:42:12,625 --> 00:42:13,785
I thought you were jealous.

621
00:42:17,385 --> 00:42:18,425
Are you really not jealous?

622
00:42:18,505 --> 00:42:19,505
I am.

623
00:42:20,305 --> 00:42:21,585
Just now,

624
00:42:23,865 --> 00:42:25,425
I saw you flirting with her.

625
00:42:26,505 --> 00:42:27,345
Me?

626
00:42:28,065 --> 00:42:29,865
How did I flirt with her?

627
00:42:29,945 --> 00:42:30,985
You did this.

628
00:42:34,305 --> 00:42:35,225
No.

629
00:42:35,305 --> 00:42:37,465
She asked me

630
00:42:37,545 --> 00:42:39,025
the directions to a café.

631
00:42:39,105 --> 00:42:40,785
So I…

632
00:42:41,745 --> 00:42:42,625
I…

633
00:42:43,105 --> 00:42:45,305
All I did was tell her it's over there.

634
00:42:47,185 --> 00:42:48,905
Couldn't you have told her properly?

635
00:42:48,985 --> 00:42:50,825
Did you have to do this?

636
00:42:54,185 --> 00:42:55,065
I'm not talking to you.

637
00:43:03,665 --> 00:43:04,505
Okay.

638
00:43:08,425 --> 00:43:09,545
Sorry to bother you.

639
00:43:09,625 --> 00:43:10,865
Can I add you on WeChat?

640
00:43:10,945 --> 00:43:13,145
Sorry, I have a boyfriend.

641
00:43:13,225 --> 00:43:14,625
Okay.

642
00:43:20,425 --> 00:43:21,905
This watermelon looks pretty good.

643
00:43:22,905 --> 00:43:25,105
-Let's go.
-What's wrong? Are you angry?

644
00:43:26,145 --> 00:43:27,025
No.

645
00:43:27,705 --> 00:43:28,905
Are you jealous?

646
00:43:29,825 --> 00:43:31,145
How is that possible?

647
00:43:31,225 --> 00:43:32,545
It's just a WeChat request.

648
00:43:32,625 --> 00:43:33,865
Why would I be jealous?

649
00:43:36,265 --> 00:43:38,665
Wait. I didn't give it to him.

650
00:43:39,585 --> 00:43:41,385
But I saw you flirting with him just now.

651
00:43:41,465 --> 00:43:42,785
When did I flirt with him?

652
00:43:42,865 --> 00:43:44,185
He didn't even ask for directions.

653
00:43:44,745 --> 00:43:47,465
You did this to him.

654
00:43:47,545 --> 00:43:48,785
What was that?

655
00:43:48,865 --> 00:43:51,185
I said, "Sorry, I have a boyfriend."

656
00:43:51,265 --> 00:43:53,545
-What do you have?
-A boyfriend.

657
00:43:55,025 --> 00:43:56,105
Present.

658
00:43:59,425 --> 00:44:00,505
Let's go.
